        },
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "Mathlib has `Polynomial.newtonMap` for Newton's method on polynomial roots in a commutative ring (and its quadratic-convergence-style theorems), but not the general analytic-Newton-via-Banach-FPT statement the article alludes to.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
