        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "describing",
          "value": "Banach FPT applied to f(x)=x+sin x on [3π/4, 5π/4]: starting from x₀=3, the iteration π = f(f(f(…f(3)…))) converges to π. Mathlib does not formalize this specific numerical example.",
          "format": "text/plain"
        }
      ],
      "target": {
        "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Banach_fixed-point_theorem?oldid=1350866762",
